    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis-relevant QoIs within ±15% of FDA experimental data across the full COU operating envelope. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed for all worst-case operating condition candidates. The computational model is deemed credible for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
